हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: After her husband Lumor’s tragic rooftop fall, Chinn was killed in the chaos — only to be reborn with memories of it all. With a second chance, she uncovers the dark conspiracies of Stacy and Camor. Armed with truth and determination, Chinn fights back to rewrite her fate and protect the one she loves.
